8231663.name: Veggie Delite Sub 6" (15 cm)
8231663.description: Crispy, crunchy, and delicious. SUBWAY Restaurant's Veggie Delite sandwich is a delicious combination of garden fresh lettuce, tomatoes, green peppers, onions, olives and pickles. Served on freshly baked bread.

8231664.name: Chatpata Chana Sub 6" (15 cm)
8231664.description: Delicious sub with a flavourful chana base patty. Will remind you of that Chatpata chaat flavour.

8231665.name: Mexican Patty Sub 6" (15 cm)
8231665.description: A refreshing filling of red and black kidney beans patty, topped with aromatic Mexican seasoning to spice up your palate.

8231666.name: Veg Seekh Sub 6" (15 cm)
8231666.description: A sub made from veg seekh kabab, enriched with the distinctive flavours of aromatic Indian spice mix.

8231667.name: Hara Bhara Kebab Sub 6" (15 cm)
8231667.description: Served on a freshly baked bread, nutritious spinach base with an abundance of exotic Indian spice mix.

8231668.name: Veg Shammi Sub 6" (15 cm)
8231668.description: A kebab specialty authentically made from lentils, enriched with the distinctive flavours of garlic and onion. Served on freshly baked bread with your choice of condiments.

8231669.name: Aloo Patty Sub 6" (15 cm)
8231669.description: The traditional aloo patty gets tastefully dressed up. A 100% potato patty seasoned with special herbs and spices with your choice of crisp fresh veggies, on freshly baked bread.

8231670.name: Veggie Patty Sub 6" (15 cm)
8231670.description: For the vegetarian who loves it livened up! This light, golden brown patty combines the flavours of the choicest carrots, bell peppers, beans and other assorted ingredients. As they say, variety is the spice of life!

8231671.name: Paneer Tikka Sub 6" (15 cm)
8231671.description: Cottage cheese slices marinated with barbeque seasoning and roasted to a light crispness. Sheer pleasure for the veggie when served on freshly baked bread.

8231672.name: Corn & Peas Sub 6" (15 cm)
8231672.description: A delicious assortment of green peas, golden corns and crunchy dices of carrot , blended in a creamy mixture of eggless mayo sauce.

8231675.name: Chicken Slice, Egg & Cheese Sub 6" (15 cm)

8231676.name: Chicken Tikka Sub 6" (15 cm)
8231676.description: A sub with ethnic flair! Boneless chicken breast pieces marinated with tikka seasoning, barbecued yet still delightfully succulent, served with your choice of condiments, on freshly baked bread.

8231677.name: Chicken Kofta Sub 6" (15 cm)
8231677.description: A tandoori classic gets a tasty makeover! Chicken that's coarsely ground is laced with a hint ofindian soices mix. Served with the choicest condiments on freshly baked bread

8231678.name: Roasted Chicken Sub 6" (15 cm)
8231678.description: Chicken breast lightly seasoned that's roasted to perfection and served with a choice of crisp veggies on freshly baked bread.

8231679.name: Chicken Tandoori Sub 6" (15 cm)
8231679.description: Succulent chicken breast pieces marinated with yoghurt, garlic , ginger and barbecued to get that delightfully unique taste .Served on freshly baked bread with creamy mint mayo sauce.

8231680.name: Chicken Slice Sub 6" (15 cm)
8231680.description: With unbeatable value and so many toppings to choose from, our hearty ham sandwich can become something new and exciting every day.

8231681.name: Italian B.M.T Sub 6" (15 cm)
8231681.description: The sandwich to conquer all hunger. Served on freshly baked bread, The Italian B.M.T. is bursting with sliced salami, pepperoni, ham and your choice of vegetables and condiments. It's a sandwich you can really sink your teeth into.

8231684.name: Turkey & Chicken Slice Sub 6" (15 cm)
8231684.description: With a sandwich this hearty you won't know you're eating low fat. Delicious sliced turkey breast and chicken ham with your choice of fresh vegetables and condiments served on freshly baked bread.

8231685.name: Tuna Sub 6" (15 cm)
8231685.description: This gift from the sea is simple, yet sumptuous ensemble of flaked tuna, mixed with mayo, and your choice of fresh vegetables. Specially built to suit the cravings of tuna lovers.

8231686.name: Subway Club Sub 6" (15 cm)
8231686.description: A delectable combination of our tender sliced turkey breast, sliced roast lamb and savory sliced chicken ham with your choice of fresh vegetables and fat-free condiments, all served on freshly baked bread. More flavor than you can imagine for under 97% Fat Free.
